912
01:09:25,220 --> 01:09:28,460
[SPEAKER_00] Vido Politeo.

913
01:09:28,460 --> 01:09:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] Mislave, recite konkretno.

914
01:09:30,000 --> 01:09:32,119
