[SPEAKER_00] bilo koji sustav.

930
01:10:05,640 --> 01:10:06,800
[SPEAKER_00] Bilo koji sustav.

931
01:10:06,800 --> 01:10:08,520
[SPEAKER_00] Predsjednički, parlamentarni,

932
01:10:08,520 --> 01:10:10,060
[SPEAKER_00] polupredsjednički.

933
01:10:10,319 --> 01:10:12,640
[SPEAKER_00] Koji god oćete izmisliti sustav.

934
01:10:12,640 --> 01:10:16,819
[SPEAKER_00] Ovoga, dvodnomni, trodobni, jednodnomni i tako dalje.

935
01:10:16,819 --> 01:10:19,939
