957
01:11:04,680 --> 01:11:06,579
[SPEAKER_00] Predsjednika, znači,

958
01:11:06,579 --> 01:11:08,079
[SPEAKER_00] sada imate u ustavu,

959
01:11:08,340 --> 01:11:09,560
[SPEAKER_00] ko ga može smijeniti,

960
01:11:09,560 --> 01:11:10,739
[SPEAKER_00] može ga smijeniti

961
