1005
01:12:38,899 --> 01:12:41,539
[SPEAKER_00] nego što ih ima premijer u ovom sustavu.

1006
01:12:41,539 --> 01:12:42,100
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, manje.

1007
01:12:42,100 --> 01:12:44,479
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, to je opet ono gdje oni vas žele

1008
01:12:44,479 --> 01:12:46,739
