1022
01:13:19,279 --> 01:13:24,420
[SPEAKER_00] da i sam predsjednik može donositi određene uredbe

1023
01:13:24,420 --> 01:13:27,500
[SPEAKER_00] sa zakonskom snagom, što ima mogućnost i tako dalje,

1024
01:13:27,500 --> 01:13:31,840
[SPEAKER_00] ali bez ikakve suglasnosti sabora.

1025
01:13:31,840 --> 01:13:34,880
[SPEAKER_00] A svi zakoni, normalno, da se dovode.

1026
01:13:34,880 --> 01:13:37,819
[SPEAKER_00] Ali da ne bismo došli u neku ekstremnu krizu vlasti,

1027
01:13:37,819 --> 01:13:42,819
